02 11:6 Then there will be a loud cry throughout the whole land of Egypt, such as has never been or will ever be again.
02 11:7 But not a dog shall growl at any of the Israelites--not at people, not at animals--so that you may know that the LORD makes a distinction between Egypt and Israel.
02 11:8 Then all these officials of yours shall come down to me, and bow low to me, saying, 'Leave us, you and all the people who follow you.' After that I will leave." And in hot anger he left Pharaoh.
