02 30:35 and make an incense blended as by the perfumer, seasoned with salt, pure and holy;
02 30:36 and you shall beat some of it into powder, and put part of it before the covenant in the tent of meeting where I shall meet with you; it shall be for you most holy.
02 30:37 When you make incense according to this composition, you shall not make it for yourselves; it shall be regarded by you as holy to the LORD.
