02 35:15 and the altar of incense, with its poles, and the anointing oil and the fragrant incense, and the screen for the entrance, the entrance of the tabernacle;
02 35:16 the altar of burnt offering, with its grating of bronze, its poles, and all its utensils, the basin with its stand;
02 35:17 the hangings of the court, its pillars and its bases, and the screen for the gate of the court;
02 35:18 the pegs of the tabernacle and the pegs of the court, and their cords;
