04 29:18 with the grain offering and the drink offerings for the bulls, for the rams, and for the lambs, as prescribed in accordance with their number;
04 29:19 also one male goat for a sin offering, in addition to the regular burnt offering and its grain offering, and their drink offerings.
04 29:20 On the third day: eleven bulls, two rams, fourteen male lambs a year old without blemish,
04 29:21 with the grain offering and the drink offerings for the bulls, for the rams, and for the lambs, as prescribed in accordance with their number;
04 29:22 also one male goat for a sin offering, in addition to the regular burnt offering and its grain offering and its drink offering.
04 29:23 On the fourth day: ten bulls, two rams, fourteen male lambs a year old without blemish,
04 29:24 with the grain offering and the drink offerings for the bulls, for the rams, and for the lambs, as prescribed in accordance with their number;
04 29:25 also one male goat for a sin offering, in addition to the regular burnt offering, its grain offering and its drink offering.
04 29:26 On the fifth day: nine bulls, two rams, fourteen male lambs a year old without blemish,
04 29:27 with the grain offering and the drink offerings for the bulls, for the rams, and for the lambs, as prescribed in accordance with their number;
04 29:28 also one male goat for a sin offering, in addition to the regular burnt offering and its grain offering and its drink offering.
04 29:29 On the sixth day: eight bulls, two rams, fourteen male lambs a year old without blemish,
04 29:30 with the grain offering and the drink offerings for the bulls, for the rams, and for the lambs, as prescribed in accordance with their number;
04 29:31 also one male goat for a sin offering, in addition to the regular burnt offering, its grain offering, and its drink offerings.
